db_schema:
Table `orders` (
  `order_id` int,
  `user_id` int,
  `product_name` varchar(100),
  `amount` decimal(10,2),
  `order_date` date,
);

Table `post` (
  `post_id` binary(16),
  `author` varchar(255),
  `contents` varchar(255),
  `created_date_time` datetime(6),
  `title` varchar(255),
);

Table `user` (
  `user_id` binary(16),
  `email` varchar(255),
  `name` varchar(255),
  `password` varchar(255),
);

Table `users` (
  `id` int,
  `user_name` varchar(50),
  `email` varchar(100),
  `signup_date` date,
)
